sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as User
  participant FE as React UI
  participant BE as FastAPI
  participant NL as NL-to-SQL Engine
  participant PG as PostgreSQL
  participant LLM as LLM
  U->>BE: Connect DB + connection string
  BE->>PG: Introspect schema (tables, cols, FKs)
  PG-->>BE: Schema stored + embedded in pgvector
  BE-->>FE: 200 OK schema ready
  FE-->>U: Render schema sidebar
  U->>FE: Ask question in chat
  FE->>BE: POST /chat/db {session, query, model}
  BE->>NL: Retrieve schema context (pgvector)
  NL->>LLM: Build SQL generation prompt
  LLM-->>NL: Generated SQL SELECT
  NL->>NL: Validate SQL (read-only check)
  NL->>PG: Execute validated SQL
  PG-->>NL: Result set
  NL-->>BE: Format + persist chat history
  BE-->>FE: Answer + SQL + source tables
  FE-->>U: Render answer with SQL shown
